<h2>Anastasios (Tasos) Sidiropoulos</h2>

<table>
<tr>
<td width="270" valign="top">
<img border=1 src="pics-main/tasos3.jpg">

<td>
<img src="pics-main/sponge5.png" style="float:right" width="250" title="From [Sidiropoulos, Singhal and Sridhar 2018]">
I am an assistant professor at the <a href="https://www.cs.uic.edu/">Computer Science</a> department in the <a href="http://www.uic.edu/">University of Illinois at Chicago</a>, where I am part of the <a href="http://theory.cs.uic.edu/">Theory Group</a>.
<br>
I did my Ph.D at the
<a href="http://web.mit.edu">MIT</a>,
advised by
<a href="http://theory.csail.mit.edu/~indyk">Piotr Indyk</a>.

